CASE WHEN COALESCE(NOPERIODUNPAID,'') = '' THEN NULL ELSE NOPERIODUNPAID  END
CASE WHEN COALESCE(DAYUNPAID,'') = '' THEN NULL ELSE DAYUNPAID  END
CASE WHEN COALESCE(BILLDAY,'') = '' THEN NULL ELSE BILLDAY  END
LEFT(CASE WHEN BLOCKDATE='1400-01-01' THEN NULL ELSE date_format(BLOCKDATE,'yyyyMMdd') END,8)
LEFT(CASE WHEN CARDOPENEDDT='1400-01-01' THEN NULL ELSE date_format(CARDOPENEDDT,'yyyyMMdd') END,8)
CASE WHEN COALESCE(INCOME,'') = '' THEN NULL ELSE INCOME  END

CASE WHEN YEAR(ASOFDATE) <= 1582 THEN ASOFDATE + INTERVAL 17 MINUTES + INTERVAL 56 SECONDS 
WHEN  COALESCE(ASOFDATE,'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7'
WHEN  YEAR(ASOFDATE) > 1582 THEN CAST(SUBSTR(ASOFDATE,1,19) AS TIMESTAMP  )
ELSE ASOFDATE END
